Log In from CRM Analytics for Android

Log in to Salesforce to explore data from your org.

Enter your user name and password, and then tap Log In.
Tap Allow to grant permission to CRM Analytics on mobile.
CRM Analytics reloads on your device, and you’ll see your pinned apps on the home screen!
